data.description: National Pinehurst Number 9 Living at its Best, with transferrable Pinehurst Country Club Charter Membership. Welcoming front porch and private backyard, this home is crafted with attention to detail inside and out. New engineered hardwood floors flow throughout light-filled living areas including updated chef's kitchen complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and pantry. Large great room with fireplace and custom built-ins plus separate formal dining room.  Primary bedroom with tray ceiling, 1 walk-in closet and ensuite with dual sinks, separate shower, and soaking tub.  Two additional bedrooms with shared bathroom. Fourth bedroom (currently being used as office) with private ensuite bath.   Three seasons porch flows out onto patio and back yard oasis.   A gorgeous saltwater pool with waterfall feature. Practice putting green and professionally landscaped grounds. 3 car garage. Upgrades include new generator, 2 Rinnai tankless water heaters, laundry room cabinets and sink, crown molding, landscape lighting, and more. Transferable PCC Charter Membership, Buyer to pay transfer fee.
